Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! All right! I'm... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but aren't you one of the guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, manager?!\NPlease come to the front desk right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was right... I'm the inn manager, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mom! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Are you okay? How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Our memories...\NOur memories are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Drim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Drim... Drim...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone's memories are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did something like that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who took our\Nmemories away is in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"T-Take them out, Roronoa Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S-See? He's being controlled by that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, someone, do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... You damn swordsman,\Nyou're always bringing in trouble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, Sanji! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now this will buy me some time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Collier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...you idiot cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, did you just... say "Luffy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So your memories are back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is scary! If your memories are back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then approach us with\Na smiling, kind face like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?!\N--Hey! Don't make it more\Ncomplicated than it already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Zoro! How dare you do that earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, do what you want, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Now we're all back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan really is wonderful, to figure out\Nthat that sea horse horn is the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! So that was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the first one to\Nget your memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude! I'm better than Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So where did that thing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's so obvious where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It turned pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It should've hurried up and escaped.\NDoes it think it's hiding wel--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! How dare you manipulate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch and fillet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, his feelings are hurt in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now, catch me if you can!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"You really piss me off! Hold it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hahaha! You can't catch me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Then how about this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm right here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"What?! No way! Now, I'm getting serious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"There, I've caught you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm not gonna let you go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're next, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to play my... trump card"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellemere-san... is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoooa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...afterimages of their memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight, you jerks?!\NI'll kick all your asses at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thanks to you guys, I even lost all the\Nmemories I collected from the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can obtain all your rich memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can become one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Become what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm not going to miss this opportunity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the one who's drowning over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"All right! I was able to\Nbecome a Millennial Dragon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--You...!\N--Amazing! You can understand what it's saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--Err...\N--Hey... This raccoon dog talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Am I a raccoon dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A talking raccoon dog and a Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And a damn bastard who almost drowned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching that dragon...\Nsomehow gets me pissed off! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? How? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon, huh? I wanna ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot? There's no\Nway you can ride it from...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know until you try... Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! My arms and legs stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He really jumped on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... What's with his body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Hey, keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow that thing looks like it's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let go of me! Hey! The memories\Nare going to leak out"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you steal our memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it saying?! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else could it be?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was finally able to become a\NMillennial Dragon! Don't interfere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,People's memories aren't yours to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna become a Millennial Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,become one by making your own big memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shut up! Take this! This is it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna fly that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I kicked its ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I remember right,\Ndon't Millennial Dragons hatch from eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can't become one\Njust by eating memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you probably don't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but we saw it with our own eyes\Nbefore we entered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, forget that. People must be\Nmaking a racket in the village by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're their benefactors who\Ngot all the villagers' memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt they're gonna treat us like heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First all-you-can-drink party\Nwe've had in a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something you wanna forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we can expect\Nthem to reward us good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a bronze statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be so popular\Nwith girls, huh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Robin? If you're able\Nto get something, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Books, as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If possible, maybe books\Non this island's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I want a medical book--\None that's this thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see the seashore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ladies and gentlemen!\NThanks for coming to greet us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Aren't we supposed to be heroes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me! I wanna ask that question myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san! Where's the waver?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Stop right there, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn memory thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn girl! Pay your bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with them?! They think we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're pirates. It can't be helped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this,\Nwe're to the point of desperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What pirate would stop just\Nbecause they're told to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A big bronze statue... It was so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...to being built... A big, dark statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that losing memories\Nwould turn into such a big fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was even some guy who\Nschemed to make us his pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Sanji-kun... I just got\Ncarried away... I just got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a damn simpleton\Nwhose body and soul got taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, if you were\Nactually standing guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this racket wouldn't have happened,\Nyou idiot Mosshead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I was sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna sleep that much,\Nsleep for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! Shut up! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you like to lose your memories again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nami-san! Please don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't gotten my memories back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...what would I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong... Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little sleepy, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just natural. Robin-chan hasn't\Nslept much because of this racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh, that's right!\N--All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a special healthy dinner with\Na mixture of herbal medicines tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, food! I forgot about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make it now, so just wait quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Say, Luffy.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come back\Nwith Zoro at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Well, I got stuck\Nunder a rock Zoro cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--A rock?!\N--Yeah. That was one huge, hard rock.
