Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, things have been settled.\NTo the next island, full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're full of hot air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think with this incident, you've all\Nlearned how important memories are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to summarize for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I feel like I just saw something\NI don't wanna remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that Split-Head is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Proud Man!\NSilver Fox Foxy"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Him again?
